# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# cyberagent .env.example
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# cyberagent is a "bring your own key" SDK. You can pass keys directly in
# code (AnalystChain(llm="gemini", api_key="...")) — this file is just a
# convenient default for the CLI / web UI, which auto-load a local .env.
# Set only what you use. NEVER commit a real .env.
#
# Market data needs NO key: stocks via yfinance.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ───── LLM providers ─────
# Pick a model in the CLI (`cyberagent` interactive menu) or with `--llm`; the
# matching API key below is auto-selected. Fill the key + (optional) model for
# each provider you want available.

# Gemini — default LLM + real-time grounding (Google Search). key: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GOOGLE_API_KEY=
GOOGLE_MODEL=gemini-2.5-pro

# OpenAI. key: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o

# Anthropic (Claude). key: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5

# DeepSeek. key: https://platform.deepseek.com/
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-chat

# ───── Roadmap (NOT yet wired — setting these has no effect today) ─────
# Planned adapters (see README roadmap): Tushare (A-share fundamentals),
# EDGAR (US filings).
# TUSHARE_TOKEN=
